ate january    political offices preceded by penny pritzker united states secretary of commerce –present incumbent current us order of precedence ceremonial preceded by sonny perdue as secretary of agriculture order of precedence of the united states as secretary of commerce succeeded by alex acosta as secretary of labor current us presidential line of succession preceded by sonny perdue as secretary of agriculture th in line as secretary of commerce succeeded by alex acosta as secretary of labor v t e united states secretaries of commerce secretaries of commerce and labor cortelyou metcalf straus nagel secretaries of commerce redfield alexander hoover whiting lamont chapin roper hopkins jones wallace harriman sawyer weeks strauss mueller hodges connor trowbridge smith stans peterson dent morton richardson kreps klutznick baldrige verity mosbacher franklin brown kantor daley mineta evans gutierrez locke bryson pritzker ross v t e current members of the cabinet of the united states trump pence acosta carson chao coatsc devos haleyc kelly lighthizerc mattis mcmahonc mnuchin mulvaneyc perdue perry pompeoc price priebusc pruittc ross sessions shulkin tillerson zinke a acting c cabinetlevel v t e cabinet of president donald trump –present cabinet secretary of state rex tillerson –present secretary of the treasury steven mnuchin –present secretary of defense james mattis –present attorney general jeff sessions –present secretary of the interior ryan zinke –present secretary of agriculture sonny perdue –present secretary of commerce wilbur ross –present secretary of labor alex acosta –present secretary of health and human services tom price –present secretary of housing and urban development ben carson –present secretary of transportation elaine chao –present secretary of energy rick perry –present secretary of education betsy devos –present secretary of veterans affairs david shulkin –present secretary of homeland security john kelly –present cabinetlevel vice president m