pacific partnership ross has said that after examining the agreement he found it was not consistent with what was advertised organizational memberships and directorshipsedit ross is a hall of fame member and past director of the turnaround management association since  ross has been the vicechairman of the board of bank of cyprus pcl the largest bank in cyprus as of january  ross was the leader or “grand swipe” of the secret wall street fraternity kappa beta phi he served on the board of trustees of the brookings institution he is also on the board of advisors of yale school of management he donated  million for the construction of evans hall at the yale school of management secretary of commerceedit secretary wilbur ross addresses to employees on march   ross in riyadh saudi arabia may  on november   it was reported by the associated press that ross would be nominated for united states secretary of commerce by incoming president donald trump the trump transition team confirmed trumps intent to nominate him on november   on february   ross was confirmed by the united states senate in a – vote in may  ross accompanied trump on his first foreign visit to saudi arabia in an interview on cnbc ross said there was not a single hint of a protester anywhere there during the whole time we were there saudi arabia banned protesting after the  arab spring and dissenters face the death penalty in  ross said that agreeing to a trade deal with the united kingdom was a low priority for the trump administration honorsedit in  ross was awarded the order of industrial service merit medal by south koreas president kim dae jung for his assistance during the  korean financial crisis ross began working with ireland and irishamerican causes starting in  with an investment in the struggling bank of ireland in recognition for his efforts on november   ross was awarded the american irish historical society gold medal at the waldorf astoria hotel new york the medal is awarded to individuals who make an especially meritorious contribution to irish american life ross was awarded the medal of the order of the rising sun gold and silver star by japanese ambassador sumio kusaka on behalf of the japanese government at kusakas new york residence on february   this was in recognition for strengthening the bonds between japan and the usa including his service as chairman of the board of new yorks japan society which had begun in  after being on its board of directors since  his work to promote and strengthen the japanese economy and his relief efforts after the  tōhoku earthquake and tsunami personal lifeedit ross married judith nodine in  they divorced in  together they had two children jessica and amanada in  he married his second wife new york lt governor betsy mccaughey they divorced in  on october   ross married his third wife hilary geary a society writer for quest magazine art collectionedit ross owns an art collection valued at  million that includes pieces ranging from western surrealists to contemporary eastern sculptures ross owns  works by rené magritte valued at  million including some of the artists most valuable paintings such as the pilgrim referencesedit  a b wilbur ross jr forbescom retrieved    boak josh november   trump taps billionaire investor ross for commerce secretary associated press retrieved  november    zarroli jim november   trump taps billionaire investor wilbur ross for commerce secretary npr retrieved november     egan matt  wilbur ross approved by senate as trumps commerce secretary cnnmoney retrieved    john parkinson january   king of bankruptcy wilbur ross grilled on trade climate change and infrastructure during confirmation hearing abc news   a b c d e f gross daniel  november  the bottom feeder king new york magazine    archived from the original on  november  retrieved  november    a b c d byrnes nanette is wilbur ross crazy december   bloomberg business week   a b c what you need to know about commerce secretary pick wilb