an society trustee of the brookings institution and chairman of its economic studies council the international board of the musée des arts décoratifs in paris the blenheim foundation the magritte museum in brussels and the palm beach civic association  he was also an advisory board member of yale university school of management secretary ross is a graduate of yale university and of harvard business school with distinction  he and his wife hilary geary ross have four children jessica ross amanda ross ted geary and jack geary work history secretary of commercedepartment of commerce last updated   social share facebook google plus twitter  bureaus  offices search by organization name or browse the tree below  type here to search  bureau of economic analysis bea bureau of industry and security bis center for faithbased and neighborhood partnerships department of commerce doc economic development administration eda economics and statistics administration esa enterprise services first responder network authority firstnet international trade administration ita minority business development agency mbda national environmental satellite data and information service nesdis national institute of standards and technology nist national marine fisheries service nmfs national ocean service nos national oceanic and atmospheric administration noaa national technical information service ntis national telecommunications and information administration ntia national weather service nws native american affairs oceanic  atmospheric research oar office of business liaison obl office of executive secretariat office of general counsel ogc office of inspector general oig office of legislative and intergovernmental affairs olia office of marine and aviation operations omao office of policy and strategic planning opsp office of public affairs opa office of the chief financial officer and assistant secretary for administration cfoasa office of the chief information officer ocio office of the chie